# 🏃‍♂️ Nutrition-Activity-BMI Analyzer

An interactive and beginner-friendly web app to help users track their **BMI**, analyze **food nutrition**, and estimate **activity-based calorie burn** — all in one place! Built using **HTML**, **CSS**, **JavaScript**, and powered by the **Nutritionix API**.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🧮 **BMI Calculator**  
  Quickly calculate your Body Mass Index and view categorized health status (Underweight, Normal, Overweight, Obese).

- 🥗 **Nutrition Analyzer**  
  Enter any food item to get real-time nutrition facts (calories, protein, fats, carbs) using the Nutritionix API.

- 🏃‍♀️ **Activity Estimator**  
  Get an estimate of calories burned from common physical activities like walking, running, cycling, etc.

- 🌐 **Responsive Design**  
  Works seamlessly on both desktop and mobile browsers.

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **API**: [Nutritionix API](https://www.nutritionix.com/business/api)

